      "content": "it just feels like i'm stuck in a room that's slowly filling with water. you can try to swim for a bit, but eventually, it's just inevitable. if the world is just going to end anyway, what's the point in staying around to watch the end? it seems more logical to just... not be part of it. like, why fight to stay when there's nothing left to fight for?",
